Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我几乎不知道奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好告诉我你对奈奈的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在心中整理好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你 也许能继续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:48.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:54.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:01:00.67,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:06.57,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:13.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:18.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:24.96,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.20,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:38.18,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:45.37,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:50.20,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.22,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:48.80,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:54.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:01:00.67,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:06.57,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:13.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:18.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:24.96,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.20,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:38.18,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:45.37,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:50.20,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.22,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 还没下课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 今天开委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没决定交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之周六和周日 哪天有空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 周六11点在车站前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉 见到他那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有些乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你搞清 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 是觉得“交往了就是我的人”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靶心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一想 事情可能发展得有些怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我让他告诉我奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好担心这种方法会不会顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得除此以外也没什么好说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她认识在初二冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三夏天因为事故和她死别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那些事里到底要判断些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么问 是要判断什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你眼前 把高桥和奈奈扔进海里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们溺水 你先救哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有这种易懂的办法就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,易懂的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说暂且吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这儿是自助的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是想确认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认矢野的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 没想到你还有那图片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊矢野 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 有矢野的待机图片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣那张 原来拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你顺利办成的拂晓 把它送你做礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 不是说删了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求了你多少次你不都说没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你怎么把待机画面删了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚田武（ドラえもん里的胖子）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO 大便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联谊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱情节？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联谊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承包公司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 去联谊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sankhon（几内亚外交官 或者别的什么吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 让我解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我说等着我一边又去联谊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是随大溜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 7月？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 够快的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 都说了是被拉去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想交别的女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之外的女人 我才看不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被矢野牵着走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天也说不了奈奈的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就当成普通的约会试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你说是讲奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可其实那条件对你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是给自己个原谅他的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己的感情再老实一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可全凭感情 也会失败吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 拘泥于奈奈的不是元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高桥你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺乏信任的话 只会得而复失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 竹内呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你 怪你不好好说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我为什么要你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 还有什么地方想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝个痛快吧 痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别垂头丧气啊 小竹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 脸皮真厚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 别说得这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在搞安慰会呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为朋友着想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说吗 要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实到今年都有两个同学向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢怎么交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往一下再喜欢不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能那样 硬来也得抢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不管怎么说 他们都是两情相悦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两情相悦 还真好听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是小美么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她发火了 就稍微耍了耍他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拼了命找元晴 上气不接下气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话 不会让她找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她找我之前 我总会先找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果然没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放弃或许还早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊 反正你们更是他的同伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没女人就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没女人撑着他就不行的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是总得有必须自己保护的东西的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 怪麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有多轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有保护的东西时人才最挺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们不知道他本人意识到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他压根就不相信女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是事情最麻烦的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是初一时吧 她老妈再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的继父 和他老妈是第一次结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎算了 今天没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是普通的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换件衣服好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 都到矢野家来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养小狗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 什么品种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂种的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被扔在竹内家的那小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个胖子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是同一只狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗也会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留神就被狗彻底缓和了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦？ 名字好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你成了个为孩子操心的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 到现在非要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都觉得没什么家庭感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想是要三个孩子 一只大狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和院子里有篮球架的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个啊 我觉得孩子一个就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 一个人就没玩伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少两个也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女各一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 要有两个男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 我又不跟你结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 捉弄到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有两个男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算爸爸出门 也有接球玩伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没和爸爸玩儿过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对爸爸的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是从母亲那听来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是我出生后就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英年早逝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野第一次和我说 他爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个游泳运动员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上学时打破过北海道大赛记录
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没完没了地说 我都快能想出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过的爸爸的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学四年时我问老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有爸爸的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照照镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 爸爸在里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十岁时的爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴和爸爸一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活泼 淘气 脑瓜聪明 帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都越来越像得不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说和我爸是一个模子刻出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个模子刻的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 好想看好想看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是矢野长大的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？有照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊谢谢 带来了呀 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着写着电话号码的名牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天再呆在这也没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那送你去车站
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再留下去 我就要输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能拉手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说不能么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说也不能kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分别的握手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多半 是让矢野焦急了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他打岔 捉弄他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在他眼前晃饵料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任的心情还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多人的话 浮现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个接一个地浮现又消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何值得犹豫的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里的意志和感情另当别论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要如何做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任需要意志的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 矛盾着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微帮我搬一下花盆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(424,444)}Félicité Parmentier
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福帕蒙提耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}帕蒙提耶 法国玫瑰育种人 1782~1847
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非 非礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天开白花的那盆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 放哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(382,444)}Constance   Spry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康斯坦斯 斯普理的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}英国著名花卉师 作家 1886~1960
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的玫瑰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候弄了这样的拱门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天粉红的玫瑰会在这里一齐绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像梦一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跃跃欲试呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不像以前那么爱说话了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学时的你可爱说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学校回来 总是把今天的事全说给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊 只是我长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸是游泳选手 在高体联赛得过冠军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也要像爸爸一样当游泳选手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你是私生子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香肠？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 矢野君他们又打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么进步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你比赛前怎么老盯着镜子看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气不好么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚精会神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要消沉嘛 都打破自己的记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没得第一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是第二吗 很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有失望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢 是我骄傲的儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴 要去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了 出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 多半是上次看望过的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈好朋友的生病的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟干尸似的真恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天你要看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 他是你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈朋友的丈夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我是美智子阿姨的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈想和人结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴也不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是需要父亲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么真正想要的总从眼前错过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留下来 却事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使讨厌 也周而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}高桥 下次好好对你说奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}所以希望你再见我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是与希望相悖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运并不长久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生总是不如所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运如果会变成不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸也会变成幸运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深信着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.03,0:25:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想奈奈一定是真的喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.27,0:25:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在一定在后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.59,0:25:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对留下你而自己去了的事悔恨交加
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.73,0:25:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对让你悲伤的事后悔得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.39,0:25:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她现在 一定在天国守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.79,0:25:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你幸福 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:20.91,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とこにいても　どんな時も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:26.55,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が消えないから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:33.92,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}消せない想い出として
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:39.87,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}受け止めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:46.32,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時はいつか深い海で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:52.18,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}青い砂になって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:59.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷めない思いと一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:12.11,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君がいない　このベッドで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:17.88,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:25.16,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寝返りをうったら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.61,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}青空が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:16:01.92,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この部屋から見える町が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:07.82,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君は好きだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:14.97,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}通り過ぎる季節が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.63,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:27.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}貝になって　話せなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:32.85,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君は海へ帰った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:40.21,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど一番近くで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.53,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日も生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:52.86,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こみあげる寂しさに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:58.45,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けそうな時は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:05.98,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少しだけ泣くから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:12.06,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこかで笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:18.30,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君がいない　このベッドで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.77,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:31.07,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}瞳をとじたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.45,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}青空が見たら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:20.91,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不论何处 不论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:26.55,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你都不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:33.92,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我愿把它当做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:39.87,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不可磨灭的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:46.32,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}时间何时在深海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:52.18,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}化作青色的砂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:59.40,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与尚未冷却的思念一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.58,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}陷入长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:12.11,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你已不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:17.88,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}床上只剩我惴惴不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:25.16,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将身子翻过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.61,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}便见到那青空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:16:01.92,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}从这房间 见到的街景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:07.82,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你曾那么喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:14.97,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}逝去的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.63,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}多么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:27.31,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}化作贝壳 无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:32.85,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你回到了大海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:40.21,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可是在最近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.53,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天你仍活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:52.86,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在要败给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:58.45,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}油然而生的寂寞时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:05.98,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我落下几滴泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:12.06,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却不知在哪欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:18.30,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你已不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.77,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}床上只剩我惴惴不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:31.07,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将眼睛闭起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.45,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}便见到那青空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:08.39,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今　君が言いかけた言葉が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:14.97,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指先にそっと降りてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:20.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何も言わなくていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:27.16,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}つないだ指をぎゅっと暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:33.98,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言葉は言葉だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:42.41,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心半分も伝えないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:50.83,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}切なくて　もどかしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:22:57.39,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕焼けが二人を包んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:04.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こみあげる胸の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:10.45,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心が痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:20.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もし君が旅人になったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:27.01,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どれくらい君を待てるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:32.69,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}季節が変わるそのたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:39.55,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}記憶が薄らぐことがあっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:46.36,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かをこんなふうに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:54.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心いっぱいで愛せないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:24:03.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}守りたい　大切な君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:09.30,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつだって二人は独りじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:16.46,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この胸が　壊れそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:23.04,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れてほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:32.78,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}切なくて　もどかしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.26,0:24:39.07,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}帰れない　このまま歩いていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:46.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指先に　感じている
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.67,0:24:53.22,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:08.39,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你方才说出的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:14.97,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻落在我的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:20.28,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}缄口不语也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:27.16,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖了紧紧相连的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:33.98,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}话语即是话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:42.41,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一半心意无法传达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:50.83,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}多么伤心 多么焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:22:57.39,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}晚霞包裹着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:04.40,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中的思念油然而生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:10.45,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:20.58,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你成为旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:27.01,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我要把你等到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:32.69,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每当季节更迭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:39.55,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}记忆都越发稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:46.36,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我无法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:54.31,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全心全意地爱一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:24:03.23,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要守护 珍重的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:09.30,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不论何时 两人都不孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:16.46,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我这颗心 即将破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:23.04,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你来抚慰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:32.78,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}多么伤心 多么焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.26,0:24:39.07,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无法回去 愿这样漫步下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:46.23,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我的指尖 感觉到那
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.67,0:24:53.22,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心的话语
